<heading>users delete - Remove a user.</heading>

<rule/>

<heading level="2">
Usage
</heading>

<pre>
  delete NAME
</pre>

<heading level="2">
Description
</heading>

<paragraph>
Deletes a user account. The account is soft-deleted: it is
marked as disabled rather than removed permanently.
</paragraph>

<heading level="2">
Examples
</heading>

<pre>
delete bob
  Delete user bob.
</pre>

<heading level="2">
See also
</heading>

<paragraph>
list, add, edit, groups, joins
</paragraph>
